column2: SELECT s.bestObjID,s.dec,str(s.ra,#,#) as ra,s.velDisp,s.velDispErr,s.velDispZ,s.velDispZErr,s.z,s.zErr,s.zWarning,p.u,p.g,p.r,p.i,p.z,p.modelMagErr_u,p.modelMagErr_g,p.modelMagErr_r,p.modelMagErr_i,p.modelMagErr_z,p.cModelMag_g,p.cModelMag_i,p.cModelMag_r,p.cModelMag_u,p.cModelMag_z,p.cModelMagErr_g,p.cModelMagErr_i,p.cModelMagErr_r,p.cModelMagErr_u,p.cModelMagErr_z FROM BESTDR9..SpecObj as s 	JOIN BESTDR9..Galaxy AS p ON s.bestObjID = p.objID 	JOIN dbo.fGetNearbySpecObjEq(#,#,#) AS b ON b.SpecobjID = S.SpecobjID WHERE  s.zWarning = # AND (s.class = &&&) AND (s.primTarget & (dbo.fPrimTarget(&&&)) > #)
